properties.areaDesc: Grand Marais to Taconite Harbor MN; Grand Portage to Grand Marais MN; Taconite Harbor to Silver Bay Harbor MN; Silver Bay Harbor to Two Harbors MN
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 5 at 9:18PM CST until January 6 at 4:00AM CST by NWS Duluth MN
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 15 to 20 knots with gusts up to 30
knots and waves 1 to 3 feet.

* WHERE...Grand Portage to Grand Marais MN, Grand Marais to
Taconite Harbor MN, Taconite Harbor to Silver Bay Harbor MN
and Silver Bay Harbor to Two Harbors MN.

* WHEN...Until 4 AM CST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Mariners, especially those operating smaller vessels, should
avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 AM CST MONDAY... ...GALE WARNING IS CANCELLED
